quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  44,40,"Hamafisina, fa ny andro ny fitsarana farany no fotoana hihaonan’izy ireo rehetra."
  44,41,"Ny andro izay tsy hilan’ny olona ny namany intsony; ary tsy ho voavonjy mihitsy izy ireo."
  44,42,"Afa-tsy, izay niantran’I Allah. Fa Izy no ilay Tsitoha, ilay be indrafo."
  44,43,"Hamafisina, fa ny hazon’ny zaqqoum (hazo mangidin’ny afobe),"
  44,44,"Dia ho sakafon’ny be fahotana."
  44,45,"Toy ny vy voarendrika hangotraka ao an-kibo."
  44,46,"Tahaka ny fangotrahan’ny rano mamay."
  44,47,"Raisonareo izy, ka avarino any anaty afo mamaivay."
  44,48,"Avy eo, tondrahinareo rano mangotraka eo ambony lohany ho famaizana azy."
  44,49,"Andramo! Fa ianao ilay nihevi-tena ho mahery, ilay manan-kaja."
  44,50,"Izany mantsy ilay nampisalasala anareo."
  44,51,"Ho amin’ny fonenana azo antoka ireo vontom-pinoana,"
  44,52,"Ao amin’ireo zaridaina sy loharano,"
  44,53,"Akanjo mangirana sy lamba lasoa no fitafin’izy ireo, ary hipetraka mifanatrika."
  44,54,"Toy izany! Ary tovovavy baribary maso no homenay ho vadin'izy ireo."
  44,55,"Hangataka karazam-boankazo am-pilaminana tanteraka izy ireo ao."
  44,56,"Tsy hanandrana fahafatesana izy ireo ao, afa-tsy ilay fahafatesana voalohany ihany. Ary harovana amin’ny famaizan’ny afo mavaivay izy ireo,"
  44,57,"Fahasoavana avy amin’ny Tomponao izany. Ary izany no fahombiazana lehibe."
  44,58,"Nataonay ho mora tamin’ny lelanao izany (Koroany), mba hahatsiaro izy ireo."
  44,59,"Koa miandrasa àry ianao, fa miandry koa izy ireo."